 of employees   website wwwtotalcom total sa french pronunciation ​tɔtal english toʊˈtæl or toʊˈtɑːl is a french multinational integrated oil and gas company and one of the seven supermajor oil companies in the world its businesses cover the entire oil and gas chain from crude oil and natural gas exploration and production to power generation transportation refining petroleum product marketing and international crude oil and product trading total is also a large scale chemicals manufacturer total is a major player in solar energy with sunpower  and total solar total has its head office in the tour total in la défense district in courbevoie west of paris the company is a component of the euro stoxx  stock market index contents  history  compagnie française des pétroles cfp –  total cfp and re branding to total –  total –present  organization  business segments  subsidiaries and affiliates of total sa  head office  senior management  group performance management committee  executive committee  operations  investments in iran  acquisitions  sponsorship  environmental and safety records  climate commitments  controversies  malta  myanmar investments  italian bribes  un oilforfood programme for iraq  bribery in iran  western sahara oil exploration  see also  references  external links historyedit total plaza the headquarters of the subsidiary total petrochemicals usa in downtown houston compagnie française des pétroles cfp –edit the company was founded after world war i when then french prime minister raymond poincaré rejected the idea of forming a partnership with royal dutch shell in favour of creating an entirely french oil company at poincarés behest col ernest mercier with the support of ninety banks and companies founded total on  march  as the compagnie française des pétroles cfp literally the french petroleum company petroleum was seen as vital in the case of a new war with germany as per the agreement reached during the san remo conference of  the french state received the  share held by deutsche bank in the turkish petroleum company tpc as part of the compensation for war damages caused by germany during world war i the french governments stake in tpc was transferred to cfp and the red line agreement in  rearranged the shareholding of cpf in tpc later renamed the iraq petroleum company in  to  the company from the start was regarded as a private sector company in view of its listing on the paris stock exchange in  the company during the s was engaged in exploration and production primarily from the middle east its first refinery began operating in normandy in  after world war ii cfp engaged in oil exploration in venezuela canada and africa while pursuing energy sources within france exploration in algeria then a french colony began in  with algeria becoming a leading source of oil in the s in  cfp introduced its downstream product – total brand of gasoline in the african continent and europe in  total petroleum north america ltd a company controlled  by cfp bought the american refining and marketing assets of vickers petroleum as part of a selloff by esmark of its energy holdings this purchase gave total refining capacity transportation and a network of  service stations in  states total cfp and re branding to total –edit the company renamed itself total cfp in  to build on the popularity of its gasoline brand later in  the name was changed to total when it became a public company listed on the new york stock exchange the french government who used to control more than  percent of the companys stock in  reduced its stake in the firm to less than  percent by  in the time period between  and  foreign ownership of the firm increased from  per cent to  per cent meanwhile total continued to expand its retail presence in north america under several brand names in  denver colorado based total petroleum total cfps north american unit purchased  road runner retail locations from texarkana texasbased truman arnold companies by  total petroleum was operating  retail stores under the vickers apco road runner and total brands that year the company began remodeling and rebranding all of its north american gasoline and convenience stores to use the total name only four years later total sold its north american refining and retail operations to ultramar diamond shamrock for  million in stock and  million in assumed debt after totals takeover of petrofina of belgium in  it became known as total fina afterwards it also acquired elf aquitaine first named totalfinaelf after the merger in  it was later renamed back to total on  may  during that rebranding the current globe logo was unveiled chart of the major energy companies dubbed big oil sorted by latest published revenue total –presentedit in  total signed for a  stake in the gas exploration venture in the kingdom of saudi arabia ksa – south rub alkhali joint venture along with royal dutch shell and saudi aramco the stake was later bought out by its partners in may  saudi aramco and total signed a mou to develop the jubail refinery and petrochemical project in saudi arabia which targeted  barrels per day bpd on  september  the two companies officially established a joint venture called saudi aramco total refining and petrochemical company satorp in which a  stake was held by saudi aramco and the balance  held by total during the  iraqi oil services contracts tender a consortium led by cnpc  which also included total  and petronas  was awarded a production contract for the halfaya field in the south of iraq which contains an estimated  billion barrels  m of oil as of  total is one of the worlds major oil companies with over  employees and operates in more than  countries in september  total announced plans to pull out of the forecourt market in the united kingdom in november  total announced it was selling its  stake and operating mandate in its nigerian offshore project to a unit of china petrochemical corp for  billion in  total started the operation at kashagan with north caspian operating company it is the biggest discovery of oil reserves since  in  total increased its stake in novatek to  in september  total and its joint venture partner agreed to buy chevron corporation’s retail distribution business in pakistan for an undisclosed amount in january  total became the first major oil and gas firm to acquire exploration rights for shale gas in the uk after it bought a  percent interest in two licences in the gainsborough trough area of northern england for  million in july  the company disclosed it was in exclusive talks to sell its lpg distribution business in france to pennsylvaniabased ugi corporation for € million  million on  october  at  mst a dassault falcon  business jet heading to paris caught fire and exploded during takeoff after colliding with a snow removal vehicle in vnukovo international airport and killing four including three crew members and ceo of total sa christophe de margerie on board alcohol presence was confirmed in the blood of the driver of the vehicle on the ground patrick pouyanne who was totals refining chief at that time was appointed as ceo after christophe de margerie died patrick pouyanné was appointed chairman of total on december   in addition to his role as ceo in february  total unveiled plans to cut  jobs in the united kingdom reduce refinery capacity and slow spending on north sea fields after it fell to a bn finalquarter loss the company said it would also sell off bn worth of assets worldwide and cut exploration costs by  total says it would still principally be an oil and gas company but aims to be  lowcarbon by  said patrick pouyanné ceo and chairman in may  in june  to expand its gas and power distribution activities total signed a m deal to buy lampiris the third largest belgian supplier of gas and renewable energy in july  total agreed to buy french battery maker saft groupe sa in a bn deal to boost its development in renewable energy and electricity businesses 