marketing assets of vickers petroleum as part of a selloff by esmark of its energy holdings this purchase gave total refining capacity transportation and a network of  service stations in  states total cfp and re branding to total –edit the company renamed itself total cfp in  to build on the popularity of its gasoline brand later in  the name was changed to total when it became a public company listed on the new york stock exchange the french government who used to control more than  percent of the companys stock in  reduced its stake in the firm to less than  percent by  in the time period between  and  foreign ownership of the firm increased from  per cent to  per cent meanwhile total continued to expand its retail presence in north america under several brand names in  denver colorado based total petroleum total cfps north american unit purchased  road runner retail locations from texarkana texasbased truman arnold companies by  total petroleum was operating  retail stores under the vickers apco road runner and total brands that year the company began remodeling and rebranding all of its north american gasoline and convenience stores to use the total name only four years later total sold its north american refining and retail operations to ultramar diamond shamrock for  million in stock and  million in assumed debt after totals takeover of petrofina of belgium in  it became known as total fina afterwards it also acquired elf aquitaine first named totalfinaelf after the merger in  it was later renamed back to total on  may  during that rebranding the current globe logo was unveiled chart of the major energy companies dubbed big oil sorted by latest published revenue total –presentedit in  total signed for a  stake in the gas exploration venture in the kingdom of saudi arabia ksa – south rub alkhali joint venture along with royal dutch shell and saudi aramco the stake was later bought out by its partners in may  saudi aramco and total signed a mou to develop the jubail refinery and petrochemical project in saudi arabia which targeted  barrels per day bpd on  september  the two companies officially established a joint venture called saudi aramco total refining and petrochemical company satorp in which a  stake was held by saudi aramco and the balance  held by total during the  iraqi oil services contracts tender a consortium led by cnpc  which also included total  and petronas  was awarded a production contract for the halfaya field in the south of iraq which contains an estimated  billion barrels  m of oil as of  total is one of the worlds major oil companies with over  employees and operates in more than  countries in september  total announced plans to pull out of the forecourt market in the united kingdom in november  total announced it was selling its  stake and operating mandate in its nigerian offshore project to a unit of china petrochemical corp for  billion in  total started the operation at kashagan with north caspian operating company it is the biggest discovery of oil reserves since  in  total increased its stake in novatek to  in september  total and its joint venture partner agreed to buy chevron corporation’s retail distribution business in pakistan for an undisclosed amount in january  total became the first major oil and gas firm to acquire exploration rights for shale gas in the uk after it bought a  percent interest in two licences in the gainsborough trough area of northern england for  million in july  the company disclosed it was in exclusive talks to sell its lpg distribution business in france to pennsylvaniabased ugi corporation for € million  million on  october  at  mst a dassault falcon  business jet heading to paris caught fire and exploded during takeoff after colliding with a snow removal vehicle in vnukovo international airport and killing four including three crew members and ceo of total sa christophe de margerie on board alcohol presence was confirmed in the blood of the driver of the vehicle on the ground patrick pouyanne who was totals refining chief at that time was appointed as ceo after christophe de margerie died patrick pouyanné was appointed chairman of total on december   in addition to his role as ceo in february  total unveiled plans to cut  jobs in the united kingdom reduce refinery capacity and slow spending on north sea fields after it fell to a bn finalquarter loss the company said it would also sell off bn worth of assets worldwide and cut exploration costs by  total says it would still principally be an oil and gas company but aims to be  lowcarbon by  said patrick pouyanné ceo and chairman in may  in june  to expand its gas and power distribution activities total signed a m deal to buy lampiris the third largest belgian supplier of gas and renewable energy in july  total agreed to buy french battery maker saft groupe sa in a bn deal to boost its development in renewable energy and electricity businesses by the  october  the company had a share value of  million euros distributed in  shares the shares are owned by a large number of shareholders the biggest being  blackrock  the employees of total sa  the company itself  the group bruxelles lambert  total has agreed to acquire billion in upstream and downstream assets from petrobras as part of the firms’ strategic alliance announced in october  for total these new partnerships with petrobras reinforce total’s position in brazil through access to new fields in the santos basin while entering the gas value chain between  and  total has organized the argos challenge a robotic competition with the aim to develop robots for their oil and gas production sites it was won by an austriangerman team using a variant of the taurob tracker robot in july  total has signed a major deal for a total amount of b with iran for the development and production of south pars the worlds largest gas field organizationedit business segmentsedit since september  total has set up a new organization to achieve its “one total” company ambition to become a responsible energy major it is composed by the following segments exploration  production gas renewables  power refining  chemicals trading  shipping marketing  services total global services total has also announced the creation of two new corporate divisions people  social responsibility human resources health safety  environment the security division and a new civil society engagement division strategy  innovation strategy  climate division responsible for ensuring that total’s strategy incorporates the  °c global warming scenario public affairs audit research  development the chief digital officer and the senior vice president technology subsidiaries and affiliates of total saedit headquarters of total cambodia in phnom penh cambodia as of  december  total sa had  subsidiaries consolidated into the group results together with significant affiliate investments and joint ventures mostly in lpg in addition total had other significant equity holdings amounting to about bn euros treated as investments and was involved in a number of significant joint ventures mostly relating to lpg and lng exploration production and shipping the joint ventures that are treated as subsidiaries are listed in the consolidated subsidiary section main consolidated subsidiaries abu dhabi gas liquefaction company ltd  united arab emirates air total international sa switzerland amyris inc  united states angola block  bv  netherlands operating in angola angola lng limited  bermuda operating in angola as  france atlantic trading  marketing inc united states atotech china chemicals ltd atotech bv netherlands atotech deutschland gmbh germany atotech taiwan basf total petrochemicals llc  united states brass holdings company limited luxembourg brass lng ltd  nigeria compagnie pétrolière de l’ouest  cpo france cosmar company  united states cosden llc united states cray valley usa llc united states cssa – chartering and shipping services sa switzerland dalia